# See https://help.github.com/articles/ignoring-files/ for more about ignoring files.

# dependencies
# Codex 지적(PR #100 2차): workspace 내부 node_modules/캐시 산출물 차단을 위해
# 재귀 패턴 사용. 루트 only 패턴(`/node_modules`)은 apps/*/node_modules,
# packages/*/node_modules 를 막지 못해 PR 에 대량 산출물 누적됨.
**/node_modules
/.pnp
.pnp.*
.yarn/*
!.yarn/patches
!.yarn/plugins
!.yarn/releases
!.yarn/versions

# testing
**/coverage
**/test-results
**/playwright-report
**/playwright/.cache

# next.js
**/.next/
**/.next-*/
**/out/

# turbo cache
**/.turbo

# production
**/build

# misc
.DS_Store
*.pem

# debug
npm-debug.log*
yarn-debug.log*
yarn-error.log*
.pnpm-debug.log*

# env files (can opt-in for committing if needed)
.env*
!.env.example

# vercel
.vercel

# typescript
*.tsbuildinfo
next-env.d.ts
.gstack/

# claude code runtime
.claude/scheduled_tasks.lock

# daily outcome (personal reports, not tracked)
/daily_outcome/

# docker postgres volume (local DB data, not tracked)
/.docker/

# playwright — workspace 재귀 패턴은 위 testing 섹션 참조 (`**/test-results` 등)
